des: Illiana's Local Choice. Playing your favorite hits all week and your favorite Classic Rock all weekend long. Tune in to listen to your favorite high school sports game and Fighting Illini Football and Basketball. Weather twice an hour, National News at the top of the hour 24/7 and local news throughout the day. You'll also be able to find daily grain and stock market reports, our National Farm Broadcaster, John Gooding, and our friends DeLoss, Rita and Jim with RFD Radio Network.
